{"tid":1971385,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"90後女教師穿著太暴露，被家長集體圍攻，老師回懟：學生喜歡就好","createTime":"2020-04-14T01:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T03:53:56.000Z","uid":23833,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b4a8cd76466c3d1a70090b5846e9ef517b516cb1","tid":1971385,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T01:09:32.000Z","msg":"師者，傳道授業解惑也。孩子上學以後，老師陪伴孩子的時間比我們父母都要長。老師的一言一行，可能比我們父母對孩子的影響會規模。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200413/0a89f98b358c4795b970a27662837afd.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20200413%2F0a89f98b358c4795b970a27662837afd.jpeg&h=b66f5b05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200413/6a0c8f4b20eb4d85a3705f46caa7f970.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20200413%2F6a0c8f4b20eb4d85a3705f46caa7f970.png&h=7f0eac41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200413/30ebc5e422854e90aa8ab79ca4d06d50.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20200413%2F30ebc5e422854e90aa8ab79ca4d06d50.jpeg&h=3dcd0333&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n作為一個人民教師，不但要注意自己的言行，舉手投足乃至穿衣打扮都會對孩子產生深遠的影響。前段時間，在群裡聊天的時候，一位叫浩浩媽媽的網友說，自己還曾經因為幼兒園老師的穿著，和老師吵了一架，差點去投訴老師。<br />\n<br />\n她說：之前自己忙著上班，一直是孩子爺爺去接送浩浩。最近休年假，她就去接浩浩放學，他發現兒子的女老師穿衣有點過分，太露，太透，擔心會把孩子帶壞的。<br />\n<br />\n於是她就和老師發信息，希望老師能夠注意自己的穿著，衣服不要穿得太短，太透，否則會影響孩子們上課的。"},{"pid":"833b56d7c0d76a705be44929130508a2d699faa1","tid":1971385,"uid":194326,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T01:12:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.anobii.com/anobi/image_book.php?item_id=016f5cf609e2b42ef3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.anobii.com%2Fanobi%2Fimage_book.php%3Fitem_id%3D016f5cf609e2b42ef3&h=f50830a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7